graph TD
    Start([Start: Cash register/<br/>Taxameter/Distance<br/>counter acquired])
    
    Start --> Check{Reporting required<br/>per ยง146a para. 4<br/>AO?}
    
    Check -->|No| NotRelevant[No notification<br/>required]
    Check -->|Yes| Collect[Collect required<br/>data]
    
    Collect --> Data[Record data:<br/>- Tax number<br/>- System serial number<br/>- Type of TSE<br/>- TSE serial number<br/>- Business location<br/>- Number of systems<br/>- Acquisition date]
    
    Data --> Deadline{Within 1 month<br/>after acquisition?}
    
    Deadline -->|No| Late[WARNING:<br/>Deadline exceeded!]
    Deadline -->|Yes| Submit[Submit notification<br/>electronically via ELSTER]
    
    Late --> Submit
    
    Submit --> Confirmation{Confirmation<br/>received?}
    
    Confirmation -->|No| Verify[Verify transmission<br/>repeat if necessary]
    Confirmation -->|Yes| Archive[Archive<br/>confirmation]
    
    Verify --> Submit
    
    Archive --> End([End: Reporting<br/>obligation fulfilled])
    NotRelevant --> End2([End])
    
    style Start fill:#90EE90
    style End fill:#FFB6C1
    style End2 fill:#FFB6C1
    style Check fill:#FFE4B5
    style Deadline fill:#FFE4B5
    style Confirmation fill:#FFE4B5
    style Late fill:#FF6B6B
    style Submit fill:#87CEEB
